<bibRefCitation author="Garrison, R. W. &amp; von Ellenrieder, N." box="[815,1216,1815,1840]" pageId="16" pageNumber="17" pagination="1 - 134" refId="ref51245" refString="Garrison, R. W. &amp; von Ellenrieder, N. (2015) Damselflies of the genus Argia of the Guiana Shield (Odonata: Coenagrionidae). Zootaxa, 4042 (1), 1 - 134. https: // doi. org / 10.11646 / zootaxa. 4042.1.1" type="journal article" year="2015">Garrison &amp; von Ellenrieder (2015)</bibRefCitation>
