<emphasis box="[611,705,1924,1948]" italics="true" pageId="16" pageNumber="17">lateralis</emphasis>
Selys to represent 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Fraser" authorityYear="1946" box="[921,1103,1924,1948]" class="Insecta" family="Coenagrionidae" genus="Argia" kingdom="Animalia" order="Odonata" pageId="16" pageNumber="17" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="infrequentula">
